name: RICHES by Taurus
description:
“What ?! ... Where?! ... Wooaahh ...”
-
Story :

This work represents a rainbow of emotions , philosophies , truths and observations ! But more than anything , you cant help but say , that IS ONE HAPPY SKULL !

My main aim with this work was to challenge myself to try and present a “Skull” one of the most used metaphors for Danger , Death , Horror and Terror ... in a way that was totally contradictory to that idea !

-Taurus
